  • 2005-09-06 13:56:07

    Are there languages installed?

    I might guess that you have set the ATutor default language to one that is not yet installed. Set the default language to English to begin with, then when you have installed other languages change the default.

    However, the fact you can refresh to display the language suggests that the problem orginated with the client system (the one the Web browser is running on). Dump your browser's cache. Or, try a different system.
